<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idce0168eb-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8" identifier="/us/usc/t47/s645"><num value="645">§ 645.</num><heading> Cost</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idce0168ec-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8" identifier="/us/usc/t47/s645/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> USF</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission may not use funds from the universal service programs of the Commission established under <ref href="/us/usc/t47/s254">section 254 of this title</ref>, and the regulations issued under that section, to pay for any costs associated with this subchapter.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idce0168ed-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8" identifier="/us/usc/t47/s645/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Other funds</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission may recover costs associated with this subchapter under <ref href="/us/usc/t47/s159">section 159 of this title</ref> to the extent provided for in an appropriation Act, as required under subsection (a) of that section.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idce0168ee-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8">(<ref href="/us/act/1934-06-19/ch652">June 19, 1934, ch. 652</ref>, title VIII, § 805, as added <ref href="/us/pl/116/130/s2">Pub. L. 116–130, § 2</ref>, <date date="2020-03-23">Mar. 23, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/238">134 Stat. 238</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
